      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i just tripped while running and my ankle is super swollen. i cant really walk on it right now without it hurting a ton. u think i should just do the rice thing (rest, ice, compression, elevation) for a couple days and see if it gets better?",
      "source": "evaluator"
